Full name (Purpose):
A data-driven ESG (Environmental, Social, Governance) investment analytics API that helps portfolio managers and ESG analysts query company metrics, analyze performance, and make informed decisions.

## Why did I pursue in such project?
- Pain: No centralised API to query company ESG metrics + financial data + portfolio-level KPIs
- Client: Portfolio manager / ESG analyst (like yourself at HKU Business School CIM)


## ESG-Score-Integration (What features do I wish to include?)



## How It Works: (What did I use to measure the KPI)

KPIs that matter:
- Portfolio average ESG score, carbon intensity
- Top/bottom performers by ESG trend
- Sector ESG distribution
- Controvery Score (Risk Flags)
- Financial vs ESG correlation (P/E, EPS vs ESG score)


